description: One of the works from the Botanica Politica series. More than a 'kembang desa', this is the national flower, but instead it is named the 'bunga bangkai'. Their genus name are Rafflesia from the family Rafflesiacecae, although Thomas Stamford Raffles was not the first to discover this flower. But he was way too happy because his name was used as the name of this flower, Rarararaplesiaaaaa…
